WEBVTT

01:26:59.899 --> 01:27:00.899
Okay, sir.

01:27:01.149 --> 01:27:02.149
What's the matter, sir?

01:27:02.858 --> 01:27:04.858
Sabu told me that Sahadevan
went to see him recently

01:27:04.899 --> 01:27:08.233
and tried to get more details
about the case.

01:27:08.524 --> 01:27:09.941
-Sabu?
-Yeah, the same old guy.
